Package com.bean

Class Underwriter

java.lang.Object
com.bean.Underwriter
public class Underwriter extends Object
The Underwriter class represents an underwriter in the vehicle insurance management system. It includes details such as underwriter ID, name, date of birth, joining date, and password.
